eo]]) ||\n|-\n| ''[[Tazza: The High Rollers]]''<ref name=tazza>{{cite web|title=Review: ''Tazza: The High Rollers''|url=https://variety.com/2006/film/markets-festivals/tazza-the-high-rollers-1200512540/|website=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]]|accessdate=2015-03-30|date=17 October 2006}}</ref> || Kwak Cheol-yong ||\n|-\n| ''Educating Kidnappers'' <!--aka A Cruel Attendance--> || Chief investigator ||\n|-\n| rowspan=6|2007 || ''[[The Old Garden]]'' || Eung-soo ||\n|-\n| ''[[Beautiful Sunday]]'' || Criminal unit chief ||\n|-\n| ''[[Small Town Rivals]]'' || Mr. Kim ||\n|-\n| ''Pacchigi! Love & Peace'' || || Japanese film\n|-\n| ''[[Hwang Jin Yi (film)|Hwang Jin Yi]]'' || Seo Gyung-deok ||\n|-\n| ''[[Epitaph (2007 film)|Epitaph]]'' || Major Akiyama ||\n|-\n| rowspan=3|2008 || ''[[Once Upon a Time (2008 film)|Once Upon a Time]]'' || Chief of State ||\n|-\n| ''Dance of the Dragon'' || Kwon Tae-san's father || Singaporean film\n|-\n| ''Ride Away'' || Im Ha-jung's father ||\n|-\n| rowspan=2|2009 || ''[[Private Eye (film)|Private Eye]]'' || Yoshioka ||\n|-\n| ''Where Are You Going?'' || Wan-bae's father ||\n|-\n| rowspan=5|2010 || ''Cafe Seoul'' || Dong-choon ||\n|-\n| ''[[Lady Daddy]]'' || Ji-hyeon's father ||\n|-\n| ''[[Happy Killers]]'' || Team leader ||\n|-\n| ''[[Man of Vendetta]]'' || Hospital chief Kim ([[Cameo appearance|cameo]]) ||\n|-\n| ''Tooku no Sora'' || Yoo Jung-bae || Japanese film\n|-\n| rowspan=2|2011 || ''[[Meet the In-Laws (2011 film)|Meet the In-Laws]]''<ref>{{cite web|first=Christopher J.|last=Wheeler|title=HanCinema's Film Review: ''Clash of the Families''|url=http://www.hancinema.net/hancinema-s-film-review-clash-of-the-families-29579.html|website=[[Hancinema]]|accessdate=2015-03-21|date=30 April 2011}}</ref> || Se-dong ||\n|-\n| ''Couples'' || Chairman Kim ([[Cameo appearance|cameo]]) ||\n|-\n| rowspan=8|2012 || ''[[Unbowed]]'' || Judge Park Bong-joo ||\n|-\n| ''[[Nameless Gangster: Rules of the Time]]'' || Prosecutor Choi Joo-dong ([[Cameo appearance|