ries)|Chief of Staff]]''\n|Jang Choon-bae\n|JTBC\n|-\n|''[[Miss Lee]]''\n|Oh Man-bok\n|tvN\n|}\n\n=== Variety show ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:700px\"\n|-\n! width=10|Year\n! Title\n! Network\n! Notes\n|-\n|2012\n| ''Come to Play'' || [[Munhwa Broadcasting Corporation|MBC]] || Panelist<ref>{{cite web|last1=Ho|first1=Stewart|title=Jay Park Joins Revamped MBC's ''Come to Play'' As Fixed Panelist|url=http://mwave.interest.me/enewsworld/en/article/13145/jay-park-joins-revamped-mbcs-come-to-play-as-fixed-panelist|website=enewsWorld|accessdate=2015-03-30|date=23 August 2012}}</ref>\n|-\n| || ''Star Junior Show'' || [[Seoul Broadcasting System|SBS]] ||\n|-\n|}\n\n== Theater ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:700px\"\n|-\n! width=10|Year\n! Title\n! Role\n|-\n| 2008 || \uc655\uad81\uc2dd\ub2f9\uc758 \ucd5c\ud6c4 ||\n|-\n| 2010 || ''Namhansanseong'' || [[Choi Myung-kil]]\n|-\n| 2012-2013 || ''Bring Me My Chariot of Fire''<ref>{{cite web|title=Cha Seung-won to expand career into play|url=http://www.asiae.co.kr/news/view.htm?idxno=2012090715262751692|website=10Asia|accessdate=2015-03-22|date=7 September 2012}}</ref> ||\n|-\n| 2013 || \uc774\uc81c\ub294 \uc560\ucc98\uac00 || Hara Bunta\n|-\n| 2014 || ''Grass 2'' || [[Jeon Bongjun]]\n|}\n \n== Awards and nominations ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" \n|-\n! Year\n! Award\n! Category\n! Nominated work\n! Result\n|-\n| 2008 || 20th Korean Culture and Entertainment Awards || Excellence Award, Actor || ''[[Bridal Mask]]'' || {{won}}\n|-\n| 2012 || [[2012 MBC Drama Awards|MBC Drama Awards]] || Golden Acting Award, Actor || ''[[Moon Embracing the Sun]]'', ''[[Dr. Jin]]'' || {{nom}}\n|-\n| 2016 || 29th [[Grimae Awards]] || Best Actor || ''The Imjin War 1592'' || {{won}}\n|-\n|2018\n|[[2018 KBS Drama Awards|KBS Drama Awards]]\n|Excellence Award, Actor in a Daily Drama\n|''[[Lady Cha Dal-rae's Lover]]''\n|{{nom}}\n|}\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist|2}}\n\n== External links ==\n* {{HanCinema person}}\n* {{KMDb person|00008222|